<h2 class="bold font-l">Hanoi Hannah</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
During the Vietnam War, North Korean broadcaster Hanoi Hannah attempts to undermine black troops by questioning why they fight overseas for a country that has such deeply-instituted racism. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>Axis Sally</span> </h3>
</div>
<div class="square_ad footer-article-ad main_2" data-isolated="0"></div>
